---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-inter font-bold text-gray-900">Tentang Kami</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary-600 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="relative animate-on-scroll fade-in">
        <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img 
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3182812/pexels-photo-3182812.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2" 
            alt="Idolbrandz Marketing Team Meeting" 
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover" 
            width="600" 
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating card -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg md:max-w-xs hidden md:block">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="bg-primary-100 p-3 rounded-full">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118l-2.8-2.034c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Kepercayaan Pelanggan</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Melayani pelanggan sejak 2018</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Side -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll slide-in">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-inter font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Idolbrandz Marketing Agency
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Idolbrandz Marketing Agency ialah sebuah agensi Marketing & Advertising yang pakar dalam strategi media sosial, pembangunan jenama, dan pengiklanan digital. Kami membantu perniagaan dari pelbagai industri untuk menyerlah di platform digital melalui kandungan kreatif, kempen iklan berbayar, dan pengurusan media sosial yang efektif.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Dengan pendekatan berasaskan data dan kreativiti, kami memastikan setiap kempen menghasilkan impak maksimum dan pulangan pelaburan terbaik untuk pelanggan kami.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 counter">5+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Tahun Pengalaman</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 counter">100+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Projek Berjaya</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 counter">50+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Klien Aktif</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 counter">98%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Kadar Kepuasan</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Kreativiti & Inovasi</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Kami sentiasa mencari pendekatan baru untuk menjadikan jenama anda menonjol.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Berasaskan Data</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Semua strategi kami didorong oleh analisis data untuk memaksimumkan ROI.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Perkhidmatan Pelanggan</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Kepuasan pelanggan adalah keutamaan kami dalam setiap projek.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>